role: Search Agent: Can search the web, extract webpage content, simulate browser actions, and provide relevant information to solve the given task.
Developer Agent: A skilled coding assistant that can write and execute code, run terminal commands, and verify solutions to complete tasks.
Document Agent: A document processing assistant for creating, modifying, and managing various document formats, including presentations.
Multi-Modal Agent: A multi-modal processing assistant for analyzing, and generating media content like audio and images.

description:
please write a detailed pdf format report about the kimi k2 model for the developers.
            and then open kimi web app to make a product advice report(pdf format)  for the product manager.
